01,899PCS Large Capacity Metal Hand Toolbox Ultimate Home Repair Master Set,inputs/reference_images/01.png,"Editorial retail product shot of the 899PCS Large Capacity Metal Hand
   Toolbox displayed exactly as shown in the reference image with all 4
   drawers open showing the complete tool set inside on a floor display
   inside a hardware and home improvement store. Match the product's
   color, texture, size, and details precisely as they appear in the
   reference. The product is the clear hero focus with open negative
   space surrounding it, nothing else nearby. No store logos, no brand
   signage, no price tags visible anywhere. Bright clean overhead
   lighting combined with cool ambient retail lighting. Background
   softly blurred with realistic retail shelving and store atmosphere
   visible in the distance. Shot on a handheld iPhone 15 Pro style
   camera with authentic casual shopper framing and slight natural
   imperfections. Visible realism: realistic textures, slight dust
   particles catching light, natural shadows, true-to-size proportions.
   Not cinematic, not studio lighting, not glossy CGI, not overly
   polished. Looks like a real customer discovered the viral TikTok
   Shop deal while browsing.","Realistic handheld iPhone 15 Pro UGC video inside a hardware and
   home improvement store. Bright clean overhead lighting with cool
   ambient retail lighting. The camera slowly moves closer to the
   899PCS Metal Hand Toolbox on the floor display as if a shopper is
   filming it for TikTok. A person's hand enters frame and lightly taps
   the toolbox while showing off the open drawers and complete tool set.
   The product remains completely still. Natural handheld motion with
   subtle camera shake, realistic lighting, casual shopper vibe,
   authentic retail environment, realistic physics. Not cinematic, not
   studio, not CGI.",image_submitted,fe_id_934898be-332d-4932-a265-18ce6ffff19d,/fx/api/trpc/media.getMediaUrlRedirect?name=5254eb7d-1f4e-48d5-8eb2-0a55369ba45b,5254eb7d-1f4e-48d5-8eb2-0a55369ba45b,/fx/tools/flow/project/54e96dd1-eb1a-40bf-9a06-10fabc82db37/edit/2529c5e8-d6d6-438c-b40b-9a75c3e41365,auto,,,,
